les enjeux et les questions de définition, de conceptualisation et de légitimation et analyse les défis que pose leur transmission. La seconde partie présente la contribution de certains savoirs locaux à la compréhension des politiques du pardon, de la justice transitionnelle, de la justice intergénérationnelle et se termine par une analyse de la « circulation » des savoirs locaux.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aEthicszAfrica, French-speaking. 0aEthnosciencezAfrica, French-speaking. 0aPolitical sciencezAfrica, French-speaking. 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aBélisle, Rachel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDijon, Xavier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFogou, Anatole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aForbi, Stephen Kizito, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIpperciel, Donald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aM'bonda, Ernest-Marie, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMbele, Charles Romain, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMbonda, Ernest-Mari, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMbonda, Ernest-Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMfouakouet, Léopold, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRondeau, Dany, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRondeau, Dany, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aY’Oole, Georges Ndumba, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2015z978311127402708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP